entries.journal_entry_description: You have your crystal. Now claim a handle and forge your first lightsaber!
entries.task01_comm_message_text: You did it on the first try. Rather impressive. You will need a handle. See Coris for an appropriate handle, and you will have your first lightsaber.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Nos'lyn sent you another message: You did it on the first try. Rather impressive. You will need a handle. See Coris for an appropriate handle, and you will have your first lightsaber.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Coris Mao has a defunct lightsaber handle that he will give to you. Go talk to him in Tatooine.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Return to Tatooine and talk to Coris Mao
